					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13599969#post-4734364</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13599969/scp-5612#post-4734364</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 30 Jul 2020 22:26:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Grigori Karpin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558017</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><em>Man's disposition is for to requite</em><br /> <em>An injury, before a benefit:</em><br /> <em>Thanksgiving is a burden and a pain;</em><br /> <em>Revenge is pleasing to us, as our gain.</em><br /> &#8212; <strong>Robert Herrick</strong></p> </blockquote> <p>This is probably obvious, but in case it is not: <em>this article fits into the overarching narrative I have started with <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4612">SCP-4612</a> and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5512">SCP-5512</a></em>.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">►&nbsp;Spoilers&nbsp;◄</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;Close&nbsp;File&nbsp;▼</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li>Watts was the sole survivor of the massacre of the <em>Society of Yorkshire Thaumaturgy</em> as described in <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4612">SCP-4612</a>.</li> <li>Watts’ obsession and drive to discover the origins of 4612-A/B led to the destruction of Clifton: as 4612-B told him to <em>do better</em>, and Watts instead spent 30 years killing and robbing people, in order to fuel his lifestyle and find out the secrets of 4612-A. If he hadn't tried to find out about the origins of 4612-A, then Watts and the town would have lived longer.</li> <li>The destruction of Clifton occurred less than 30 years after the massacre in York, and 4612-B is still incredibly enraged by the death of his father.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Crit</span>:<br /> Reads: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5986843&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="Ralliston" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5986843)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston" >Ralliston</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thismightbeauto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6644559&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="ThisMightBeAuto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6644559)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thismightbeauto" >ThisMightBeAuto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5231418&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="Popsioak" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5231418)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" >Popsioak</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6394107&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="chiifu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6394107)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" >chiifu</a></span>, <span class="error-inline"><em>The Crying Warmonger</em> does not match any existing user name</span><br /> In-depth: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/caspian2" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5343993&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="caspian2" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5343993)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/caspian2" >caspian2</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" >HarryBlank</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1787775&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="Riemann" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1787775)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" >Riemann</a></span></p> <p>And <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedagon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5903100&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998824" alt="Pedagon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5903100)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedagon" >Pedagon</a></span>, for being stubborn and really slapping me in the face with a desperately needed rearrangement of the pacing in this, without that it was half the article it is.</p> <hr /> <p>If you would like to see other articles I have written: <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/grigori-karpin-s-author-page">My Author Page</a></p> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/hecatoncheires-cycle-hub">Hecatoncheires Cycle</a></strong></p> </div> 
